FuncDef: This command controls the behavior of QinQ SAP y.0 (for example, 1/1/1:3000.0). If the flag is not enabled (no new-qinq-untagged-sap), the y.0 SAP works the same as the y.* SAP (for example, 1/1/1:3000.*); all frames tagged with outer VLAN y and no inner VLANs or inner VLAN x where inner VLAN x is not specified in a SAP y.x configured on the same port (for example, 1/1/1:3000.10).
